{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fc5-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4717"},"text":"§ 4717.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Enforcement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fc6-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fc7-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 180 days after the appointment and qualification of the Administrator, the Fund shall promulgate such regulations as may be necessary to carry out this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fc8-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations required","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The regulations promulgated under paragraph (1) shall include regulations applicable to community development financial institutions that are not insured depository institutions to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fc9-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717/a/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" prevent conflicts of interest on the part of directors, officers, and employees of community development financial institutions as the Fund determines to be appropriate; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fca-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717/a/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" establish such standards with respect to loans by a community development financial institution to any director, officer, or employee of such institution as the Fund determines to be appropriate, including loan amount limitations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fcb-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4717/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Administrative enforcement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The provisions of this subchapter, and regulations prescribed and agreements entered into under this subchapter, shall be enforced under section 8 of the Federal Deposit Insurance Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1818"},"text":"12 U.S.C. 1818","children":[],"tail":"] by the appropriate Federal banking agency, in the case of an insured community development financial institution. A violation of this subchapter, or any regulation prescribed under or any agreement entered into under this subchapter, shall be treated as a violation of the Federal Deposit Insurance Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1811"},"text":"12 U.S.C. 1811","children":[],"tail":" et seq.]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddd3b2fcc-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/325/tI/s119"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–325, title I, § 119","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-09-23"},"text":"Sept. 23, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/2188"},"text":"108 Stat. 2188","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddd3b2fcd-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddd3b2fce-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddd3b2fcf-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Federal Deposit Insurance Act, referred to in subsec. (b), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-09-21/ch967/s2"},"text":"act Sept. 21, 1950, ch. 967, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/873"},"text":"64 Stat. 873","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 16 (§ 1811 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1811"},"text":"section 1811 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddd3b2fd0-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/325/s119"},"text":"section 119 of Pub. L. 103–325","children":[],"tail":". Subsec. (c) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/325/s119"},"text":"section 119 of Pub. L. 103–325","children":[],"tail":" amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t18/s657"},"text":"section 657 of Title 18","children":[],"tail":", Crimes and Criminal Procedure."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
